title Complete Publisher-Subscriber Cycle (User View)

actor User
participant "R: Runtime" as Runtime
participant "OfferedProducer<R>" as OfferedProducer
participant "Consumer<R>" as Consumer
participant "Publisher<T, R>" as Publisher
participant "Subscription<T, R>" as Subscription

User -> Runtime: Build and initialize runtime
Runtime --> User: R instance

User -> Runtime: producer_builder() & build()
Runtime --> OfferedProducer: OfferedProducer<R>

User -> OfferedProducer: offer()
OfferedProducer --> User: Offered (service discoverable)

User -> Runtime: find_service() & get_available_instances()
Runtime --> Consumer: Consumer<R>

User -> Consumer: event.subscribe(capacity)
Consumer --> User: Subscription<T, R>

Note over User, Subscription: Data exchange phase

loop Publish-Subscribe Cycle
    User -> OfferedProducer: event_name
    OfferedProducer --> Publisher: Publisher<T>

    User -> Publisher: allocate() & write(data) & send()
    Publisher --> User: Result<()>
    Note over User: Data sample sent

    User -> Subscription: try_receive(&mut container)
    Subscription --> User: Result<usize>

    User -> User: pop_front() & deref & read data
end

Note over User, Subscription: End of data exchange phase

User -> OfferedProducer: unoffer()
Note over User: Service unregistered
OfferedProducer --> User: Producer<R>


@enduml
